Adcorp Says Full-Year Normalised Earnings Per Share to Fall as Much as 9%

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-10T10:53:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/adcorp-says-full-year-normalised-earnings-per-share-to-fall-as-much-as-9-.html
Adcorp Holdings Ltd. (ADR)  said normalised
earnings per share for the 12 months to Feb. 28 are expected to
fall by between 7 percent and 9 percent from a year earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
